  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252790/extras/3ebcc7a1a961bde084ce27654a8a351f.avif?t=1704785741\" width=600 height=94 /></span><br>Your friend has been infected again, find a cure before time runs out. But it won't be easy, sooner or later your friend will relapse and you'll have to find a new cure in a new randomly generated mansion. Will you be able to discover the secret of the mansion and save your friend once and for all?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252790/extras/708a1485b8dd1df1f2b459ebcb35adc6.poster.avif?t=1704785741\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252790/extras/708a1485b8dd1df1f2b459ebcb35adc6.webm?t=1704785741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252790/extras/708a1485b8dd1df1f2b459ebcb35adc6.mp4?t=1704785741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Vaccine Rebirth has been built from scratch, expanding the original idea, including new gameplay mechanics, enemies, locations, weapons and much more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252790/extras/9e89aa881de88977dbba81cef3f94b3b.poster.avif?t=1704785741\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252790/extras/9e89aa881de88977dbba81cef3f94b3b.webm?t=1704785741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252790/extras/9e89aa881de88977dbba81cef3f94b3b.mp4?t=1704785741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Share the fear playing in the new local cooperative mode or beat the best online records of other survivors.<br><br>Enter once again into the world of Survival Horror.",
